Two Plant doors can be found in the underwater area, which act as a barrier of entry to the different activities found in the area. They provide a small amount of Agility experience when first passed, but subsequent passing of the plant doors will not grant experience. Moving away some distance will reset this inability to get experience again.

Two '''Plant doors''' can be found in the [[underwater]] area, which act as a barrier of entry to the different activities found in the area. They provide a small amount of [[Agility]] experience when first passed, but subsequent passing of the plant doors will not grant experience. Moving away some distance will reset this inability to get experience again.
